```

Messages appear instantly.

---

### Online Status

```text
Online
Offline
```

---

### Message History

Store chats in database.

---

## Technologies

### Backend

* Python
* FastAPI or Flask

### Database

* MongoDB or PostgreSQL

### Real-Time

* WebSockets

---

## Why Recruiters Like It

Demonstrates:

✅ Networking

✅ APIs

✅ Databases

✅ Real-time systems

